OL,3,CCritical Incident declared at Bristol
OL,4,Cand Weston-super-Mare hospitals
OL,6,FThree major hospitals in Bristol,
OL,7,Falong with another in North Somerset,
OL,8,Fhave declared a Critical Incident
OL,9,Fbecause of "significant pressures" on
OL,10,Ftheir services.
OL,12,FThe Bristol Royal Infirmary, Bristol
OL,13,FRoyal Hospital for Children, and St
OL,14,FMichael's maternity hospital, along
OL,15,Fwith Weston General are all being
OL,16,Fimpacted.
