OL,3,CCritical Incident declared at Bristol
OL,4,Cand Weston-super-Mare hospitals
OL,6,FThey are all part of the University
OL,7,FHospitals Bristol and Weston NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust (UHBW) which is now
OL,9,Fin its second day at Critical Incident
OL,10,Flevel.
OL,12,FProfessor Stuart Walker, Managing
OL,13,FDirector at UHBW Trust, said that all
OL,14,Fsites within Bristol are currently
OL,15,Fexperiencing "exceptionally high
OL,16,Fdemand".
OL,18,F"We are working closely with our
OL,19,Fsystem partners to help ease these
OL,20,Fpressures," he said.
