OL,6,F"If you need urgent medical help and
OL,7,Fare unsure where to go, please contact
OL,8,FNHS 111 for advice."
OL,10,FWhat is a 'Critical Incident'?
OL,12,FHospitals can declare a Critical
OL,13,FIncident when they face extraordinary
OL,14,Fpressure and are unable to function as
OL,15,Fusual.
OL,17,FIt means the hospital can direct more
OL,18,Fresources - such as staff and money -
OL,19,Finto their emergency department.
